# üöÄ SONIC WORKFLOW SETUP GUIDE
# ‚ö†Ô∏è **HIGH VRAM WARNING:** This workflow requires substantial GPU memory to run properly.

## üì• STEP 1: INSTALL NODES
> Go to **Manager > Custom Nodes Manager** and install:
- ComfyUI_Sonic
- ComfyUI-VideoHelperSuite
- ComfyUI-Easy-Use
- WAS Node Suite
> **‚ö†Ô∏è IMPORTANT:** Restart ComfyUI after installation

## üíæ STEP 2: DOWNLOAD & ORGANIZE MODELS

### üìÇ MAIN FOLDER: `ComfyUI/models/sonic/`
Download these files and place them directly in the sonic folder:
- üì• [audio2bucket.pth](https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1jI32B-2JX17seSGG0-MnZgUhCMHCEZlx)
- üì• [audio2token.pth](https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1jI32B-2JX17seSGG0-MnZgUhCMHCEZlx) 
- üì• [unet.pth](https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1jI32B-2JX17seSGG0-MnZgUhCMHCEZlx)
- üì• [yoloface_v5m.pt](https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1oe8VTPUy0-MHHW2a_NJ1F8xL-0VN5G7W)

### üìÇ SUBFOLDER: `ComfyUI/models/sonic/RIFE/`
1. First, create this subfolder
2. Download and place inside RIFE folder:
   - üì• [flownet.pkl](https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1QIIDvCDU-rp1ZB8qDA6NQqVn8F9WYMhE)

### üìÇ SUBFOLDER: `ComfyUI/models/sonic/whisper-tiny/`
1. First, create this subfolder
2. Download from here [https://huggingface.co/openai/whisper-tiny/tree/main](https://huggingface.co/openai/whisper-tiny/tree/main) these 3 files and place inside whisper-tiny folder:
   - üì• config.json
   - üì• model.safetensors
   - üì• preprocessor_config.json

### üìÇ SVD CHECKPOINT: `ComfyUI/models/checkpoints/`
1. **Choose ONE** of these Stable Video Diffusion models:
   - üì• [svd_xt.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/stable-video-diffusion-img2vid-xt/tree/main) (Larger, ~ 9.56 GB)
   - üì• [svd_xt_1_1.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/stable-video-diffusion-img2vid-xt-1-1/tree/main) (Smaller, ~ 4.78 GB
)

2. **Hugging Face Access Steps:**
   - You must be logged into Hugging Face to download
   - Click the "Expand to review and access" button
   - Read the license agreement
   - Enter your name and email
   - Accept the terms of use
   - Now you can download the model file

3. Place the downloaded SVD file in `ComfyUI/models/checkpoints` folder

---
